	(hildon_desktop_popup_menu_init,
	hildon_desktop_popup_menu_update_scroll_buttons,
	hildon_desktop_popup_menu_scroll_cb): correctly update the state of
	scroll buttons depending on the position of the scrolling.
	Fixes NB#65438.

